<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idee198804-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s178l"><num value="178l">§ 178l.</num><heading> Rules and regulations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretaries may issue rules and regulations necessary to effectuate the purposes of this subchapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idee198805-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/95/592/s14">Pub. L. 95–592, § 14</ref>, <date date="1978-11-04">Nov. 4, 1978</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/92/2533">92 Stat. 2533</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/98/284/s13">Pub. L. 98–284, § 13</ref>, <date date="1984-05-16">May 16, 1984</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/98/184">98 Stat. 184</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
