<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idee198808-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1984—<ref href="/us/pl/98/284">Pub. L. 98–284</ref> substituted “The Secretaries” for “The Secretary of Agriculture and the Secretary of Commerce”.</p>
